author: OpenAI
description:
We’re releasing a new version of ChatGPT Images⁠, powered by our new flagship image generation model. 

Now, whether you’re creating something from scratch or editing a photo, you’ll get the output you’re picturing. It makes precise edits while keeping details intact, and generates images up to 4x faster. 

Alongside, we’re introducing a new Images feature within ChatGPT, designed to make image generation delightful—to spark inspiration and make creative exploration effortless.

The new Images model and feature are rolling out today in ChatGPT for all users, and in the API as GPT Image 1.5.
title: ChatGPT Images
